<HEADLINE> UNICEF to Help Nigeria Improve Basic Education </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, December 7 (Xinhua) -- Nigeria and the United Nations
Childrens's Fund (Unicef) have agreed to cooperate in enhancing
the capacity of local communities in the country to plan and
manage basic education.
</P>
<P>
A Nigerian television authority report said tonight that both
parties set off strategies that include the increase and
enrollment of girls in the eight northern states from 30 to 60
