today with chairman of the Organization of African Unity (OAU),
Zimbabwean president Robert Mugabe.
</P>
<P>
Upon returning here from his one and half hours of talks with
Mugabe, Chiluba said they discussed the October 28 attempted coup
in his country.
</P>
