dealing with political strife, or face tough action from
government.
</P>
<P>
Buthelezi warned that if a spirit of tolerance was not
cultivated before next year, South Africans could expect many
problems in 1999. He said only if the IFP was in govenrment after
1999 could a unified leadership necessary for the promotion of
economic prosperity and stability be provided. 
</P>
