calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Frankfurt: min. -2 degrees C., max. 2 degrees C., overcast,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Paris: min. 3 degrees C., max. 7 degrees C., overcast to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
London: min. 6 degrees C., max. 9 degrees C., drizzle, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
New York: min. 1 degree C., max. 6 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.  
</P>
