Iranian-Kuwaiti ties after returning from the OIC ministerial
meeting which ended here Sunday.
</P>
<P>
He said that the recent Gulf tour by Iranian Foreign Minister
Kamal Kharrazi resulted in bolstering the ties between Iran and
the Gulf Cooperation Council states.
</P>
<P>
