park will give priority to electronic information, biological
technology, high-efficiency, energy-saving and new-material
industries, an official said, adding that the companies would
receive favorable policies.
</P>
<P>
"They can also enjoy quality service in computer networks,
loan-extensions, communication and joint-research in science and
technology," he said.  
