<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 8 (Xinhua) -- The Eighth Beijing Municipal
Congress of the Communist Party of China (CPC) will be convened
on Dec. 12, according to an organizing department of the congress.
</P>
<P>
In accordance with the essence of the 15th National CPC
Congress held in September, the week-long session will summarize
the work in the past five years and establish major goals for the
capital's development in the next five years.
</P>
