<BODY>
<HEADLINE> PLA Delegation Back Home </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 8 (Xinhua) -- A military goodwill delegation
of the Chinese People's Liberation Army (PLA), led by Wen Zongren,
political commissar of the PLA Lanzhou Military Area Command,
returned to Beijing today after winding up a goodwill visit to
Namibia, Mauritania and Morocco. 
</P>
</TEXT>
